creator: American University of Beirut
descriptionHtml:
The AUB Alumni App allows alumni to tap into AUB’s worldwide community, stay connected and up-to-date with the latest news from #AUB and other alumni, and streamline communications with the Office of Alumni Relations.


What AUB alumni can do through the App:



- Stay up-to-date on the latest alumni happenings and news!

- Check out – and sign up for – alumni events

- Communicate easily with other registered alumni

- Find useful information about WAAAUB chapters, FAQs, and important alumni links

- Submit suggestions

- Reach out and connect with the Office of Alumni Relations



And that’s just the beginning… will be making ongoing improvements and adding additional features soon.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We've got BIG news! Over the past couple of months we've been busy working on a revamped app experience, and we're excited to finally share it with you! Experience AUB app with a whole new revamped UI/UX, and new AUB branding!

What's more?

We've also completely revamped the forms feature..

You get the picture. A whole new app at your fingertips and we can't wait to see you interact with it!
